## Phase 5: Documentation

### 5.1 Create Supplementary Documentation

**Location:** `llms-static/Daisy[ControlName].md`

This is a REQUIRED step for all new controls. Follow the workflow in `llms-static/WORKFLOW.md`:

```markdown
